1,000,000,000,000 Tokens Total:

10% DEV WALLET (80% LOCKED RELEASES OVER 6 MONTHS)

40% PRESALE

45% LIQUIDITY

5% ECOSYSTEM AND MARKETING

TOKEN BURN

4% of tokens burn forever during every transaction

HOW IT WORKS?

$CHAD has a 10% tax or slippage fee on all transactions to prevent price manipulation and encourage holding.
1% from that goes into LP for liquidity.
4% gets burned forever.
4% goes back to all the $chad holders.
And 1% will be used for community fund (CEX listings)

CEX LISTING FUND

1% of the burn goes to the community fund that will allow us to list on CEX listings and get us on the road to Binance

TOKEN REDISTRIBUTION

4% of the tokens get redistributed to wallet holders according to their weighted holdings

AUTOMATED LP

1% of tokens that are part of the slippage are added into the LP. This is to make sure liquidity is never thin like the virgin.
